WEBVTT

00:02:29.697 --> 00:02:33.362
Most of the children we had removed
from the orphanage

00:02:33.386 --> 00:02:36.896
were not, in fact, orphans at all.

00:02:38.013 --> 00:02:39.490
They had parents,

00:02:40.547 --> 00:02:43.918
and the few that were orphaned
had other living relatives,

00:02:43.942 --> 00:02:46.462
like grandparents and aunties and uncles

00:02:46.486 --> 00:02:48.062
and other siblings.

00:02:48.885 --> 00:02:53.317
So why were these children
living in an orphanage

00:02:53.341 --> 00:02:55.687
when they weren't orphans?

